\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}}+\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}}\ge \sqrt{a},a \gt0\quad?
\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}} + \sqrt{\frac{a}{2}} = 2\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}} = \frac{2}{\sqrt{2}}\sqrt{a}
\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}} + \sqrt{\frac a2} = 2 \frac{\sqrt a}{\sqrt 2} = \frac {2}{\sqrt 2} \sqrt{a} = \sqrt 2 \sqrt a = \sqrt{2a} > \sqrt a
\sqrt a(\sqrt {\frac 12}+\sqrt {\frac 12})=\sqrt 2 \sqrt a \gt \sqrt a
\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}} + \sqrt{\frac{a}{2}} = 2\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}} = \frac{2}{\sqrt{2}}\sqrt{a}\geq \sqrt{a}
\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}}+\sqrt{\frac{a}{2}}\ge\sqrt{a} \; \wedge \; a>0
\Leftrightarrow \; 2\frac{\sqrt{a}}{\sqrt{2}}\ge\sqrt{a} \; \wedge \; a>0
\Leftrightarrow \; 2\frac{\sqrt{2}\sqrt{a}}{2}\ge\sqrt{a} \; \wedge \; a>0
\Leftrightarrow \; \sqrt{2}\sqrt{a}\ge\sqrt{a} \; \wedge \; a>0
\Leftrightarrow \; \sqrt{2}\ge1 \; \wedge \; a>0
